# Mobile: Native Android (Index)

## Rule files (by concern)

- `architecture.mdc`: layer boundaries (core/infrastructure/presentation)
- `ui.mdc`: UI boundaries (no business logic in UI)
- `performance.mdc`: memory management, coroutines, background work
- `networking.mdc`: Retrofit, OkHttp, error handling
- `state.mdc`: ViewModel, LiveData, StateFlow patterns
- `error_handling.mdc`: sealed classes, Result types, exception handling
- `accessibility.mdc`: TalkBack, content descriptions, a11y support
- `testing.mdc`: testing expectations
- `security.mdc`: no secrets, safe logging, safe auth changes
